--- !u!114 &795407339
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 795407337}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2520540c7e0f5054bbc0412025237cbb, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TextSwitch
  texts:
  - 'WASD: Movement\r\nQ, E: Swap tool\r\nLMB: Use tool\r\nShift: Sprint\r\n'
  - 'Use the hoe to till dirt by holding it down. Then select the seed in your inventory
    and click the tilled dirt to plant it.\r\nUse the watering can to water planted
    seeds. Watered seeds grow twice as fast, although the speed increase decreases
    with time.\r\nThe shovel has 3 uses. 1: Move a fully grown plant once by clicking
    on it with LMB. Sell fully grown plants by pressing control+LMB. 3: Attack enemies
    by pressing space. Your attacks can be stalled by holding down LMB, allowing
    you to aim it.'
  - Waves of enemies will appear every minute. The longer you survive the more enemies
    appear.\r\nThe enemies will attempt to reach your home and destroy it, if they
    succeed you lose the game and are forced to restart on day 1.
  - When your plants are fully grown they will aid in the defense of your home. You
    can move a fully grown plant once using your shovel.
  - You can gain money by killing enemies or selling fully grown plants. The value
    of a fully grown plant decreases the more time you take before selling it. Your
    money can be spent at a shop that appears outside your home at the start of each
    day.
  display: {fileID: 795407340}
  currect: 0
  gsManager: {fileID: 0}
